pageContext.claim: “We have more in this arena, and I hate to say this to you, we have more than this outside of the arena trying to get in. So if you'd like to give up your seat or where you're standing, sorry, we couldn't get you seats, but if you want to give it up, let them come in. You go out.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump did pack out the Manchester arena but photos and videos do not appear to show more people outside the arena than inside.
